2014年，嘎嘎称她在19岁时被性侵，为此她接受了精神和物理治疗<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2014/dec/02/lady-gaga-reveals-she-was-raped|title=Lady Gaga reveals she was raped at 19|first1=Larney|date=2014-12-02|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|accessdate=2014-12-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141219013644/http://www.theguardian.com/music/2014/dec/02/lady-gaga-reveals-she-was-raped|archivedate=2014-12-19|last1=Bakare}}</ref>，因此事她患上了[[创伤后压力综合征|创伤后压力综合征]]，并表示医生、家人和朋友的支持帮助了她<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-38218247|title=Lady Gaga says she has PTSD after being raped at 19|date=2016-12-05|publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|accessdate=2016-12-10|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161208152031/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-38218247|archivedate=2016-12-08}}</ref>。

=== 2005年–2007年：事业起步 ===
