2005年，卡卡與嘻哈歌手{{tsl|en|Melle Mel|梅勒·梅爾}}為附贈於奎迪克·凱西的兒童小說《公園入口》的[[有聲書|有聲書]]錄製了兩首歌。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.villagevoice.com/blogs/lady-gaga-did-a-childrens-book-in-2007-6374841|title=Lady Gaga Did a Children's Book In 2007!|date=2010-01-19|work=[[The_Village_Voice|The Village Voice]]|last=Musto|first=Michael|accessdate=2010-01-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151105150228/http://www.villagevoice.com/blogs/lady-gaga-did-a-childrens-book-in-2007-6374841|archivedate=2015-11-05}}</ref> 她同時也與紐約大學的朋友組成了樂團SG Band<ref name="growingupgaga"/>{{sfn|Morgan|2010|page=31}} 樂團於紐約各地演出，成為了下東區俱樂部的固定班底。<ref name="growingupgaga">{{cite magazine|first=Vanessa|last=Grigoriadis|author-link=Vanessa Grigoriadis|title=Growing Up Gaga|date= 2010-03-28|url=https://nymag.com/arts/popmusic/features/65127|magazine=[[New_York_(magazine)|New York]]|access-date=2010-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100401055337/http://nymag.com/arts/popmusic/features/65127/|archive-date=2010-04-01}}</ref> 在2006年6月於音樂表演場地{{tsl|en|The Cutting Room}}舉辦的{{tsl|en|Songwriters Hall of Fame|詞曲作者名人堂}}展示出新的作詞人名單時，卡卡被人才偵察員溫蒂·斯塔蘭引薦給製作人{{tsl|en|Rob Fusari|羅布·富薩里}}。<ref name=Fusari1>{{cite news|last=Kaufman|first=Gil|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1634292/lady-gaga-rob-fusari-lawsuit-a-closer-look/|title=Lady Gaga/ Rob Fusari Lawsuit: A Closer Look|publisher=MTV News|date=2010-03-19|accessdate=2013-10-08|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141003020556/http://www.mtv.com/news/1634292/lady-gaga-rob-fusari-lawsuit-a-closer-look/|archivedate=2014-10-03}}</ref> 富薩里與在紐澤西一日遊的卡卡合作，幫助她發展她的音樂並編製新的素材。{{sfn|Morgan|2010|page=36}} 製作人聲稱與卡卡於2006年5月開始約會，並自稱是第一名稱呼她從[[皇后樂團|皇后樂團]]的歌曲《{{tsl|en|Radio Ga Ga}}》派生出的名稱「女神卡卡」的人。<ref name=Fusari2>{{cite magazine|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/958922/lady-gaga-sued-by-producer-rob-fusari|title=Lady Gaga Sued By Producer Rob Fusari|magazine=[[Billboard_(magazine)|Billboard]]|accessdate=2013-10-08|date=2010-03-18|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130915020236/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/958922/lady-gaga-sued-by-producer-rob-fusari|archivedate=2013-09-15}}</ref> 而這段感情最後結束於2007年1月。<ref name="rsannual">{{cite magazine|last=Hiatt|first=Brian|date=2009-05-30|title=The Rise of Lady Gaga|magazine=Rolling Stone|location=New York|volume=1080|issue=43|issn=0035-791X}}</ref>

