富薩里和卡卡成立了一間有限責任公司Team Lovechild以便促進她的音樂事業。<ref name="Fusari2"/> 他們錄製[[電音流行|電音流行]]歌曲，並將其寄送至音樂產業高層管理部門。約書亞·薩魯賓，[[Def_Jam唱片公司|Def Jam唱片公司]]的[[A&R|A&R]]管理者對兩人的作品給予正面評價，在薩魯賓的老闆{{tsl|en|L.A. Reid|安東尼奧·瑞德}}表示同意時，卡卡於2006年9月在Def Jam面試演唱，然而被簽下後卡卡卻從未和瑞德見面:「我常常在他的辦公室外等好幾個小時，希望他和我談談我的音樂理念等等，但他從來沒有這麼做，甚至連出來見我一面都沒有過。」<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.michigandaily.com/content/lady-gaga-new-ep|title=Lady Gaga unleashes an electro-pop 'Monster'|last=Resende|first=Sasha|date=2009-12-09|accessdate=2014-06-27|work=[[The_Michigan_Daily|The Michigan Daily]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141024034658/http://www.michigandaily.com/content/lady-gaga-new-ep|archivedate=2014-10-24}}</ref>{{sfn|Morgan|2010|page=45}} 在被公司放任不管3個月後，<ref name="Allmusic bio">{{cite web|url={{Allmusic|class=artist|id=lady-gaga-p1055684 |pure_url=yes}} |title=Lady Gaga |last=Birchmeier |first=Jason |date=2008-04-20 |publisher=[[AllMusic|AllMusic]] |accessdate=2010-01-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101021072619/http://www.allmusic.com/artist/lady-gaga-p1055684 |archivedate=2010-10-21 }}</ref> 她回鄉與家人共度聖誕節。在她直率的個性下，她開始於新藝術秀上表演。<ref name='always-famous'>{{cite news|title=Lady Gaga: 'I've always been famous, you just didn't know it'|date=2010-02-16|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/rockandpopfeatures/7221051/Lady-Gaga-Ive-always-been-famous-you-just-didnt-know-it.html|work=[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]]|last=Carlton|first=Andrew|accessdate=2011-02-09|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110131220615/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/rockandpopfeatures/7221051/Lady-Gaga-Ive-always-been-famous-you-just-didnt-know-it.html|archivedate=2011-01-31}}</ref> 在此同時，她遇見了後期為她塑造舞台形象的[[行為藝術|行為藝術家]]{{tsl|en|Lady Starlight|星光夫人}}。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Montgomery|first1=James|title=Lady Gaga's 'Inside The Outside': Meet The 'Perpetual Underdog'|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1664600/lady-gaga-inside-the-outside-show-preview/|publisher=MTV News|accessdate=2017-10-29|date=2011-05-25|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171029174614/http://www.mtv.com/news/1664600/lady-gaga-inside-the-outside-show-preview/|archivedate=2017-10-29}}</ref> 這對組合開始在城裡的酒吧如{{tsl|en|Mercury Lounge}}、{{tsl|en|The Bitter End}}和{{tsl|en|Rockwood Music Hall}}演出，她們使用藝名於現場表演，並以「女神卡卡與星光表演劇」著稱。號稱「終極流行藝術搖滾秀」的她們行為一向帶有低調的向1970年代致敬的味道。<ref name="seattleweekly">{{cite news|url=http://www.seattleweekly.com/2008-11-19/music/lady-gaga-some-like-it-pop/|title=Lady GaGa: Some Like it Pop|last=Hobart|first=Erika|date=2008-11-18|work=[[Seattle_Weekly|Seattle Weekly]]|accessdate=2009-01-10|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090109192648/http://www.seattleweekly.com/2008-11-19/music/lady-gaga-some-like-it-pop|archivedate=2009-01-09}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bmi.com/news/entry/535267|title=Lady Gaga|date=2007-07-09|publisher=[[Broadcast_Music_Incorporated|Broadcast Music Incorporated]]|accessdate=2009-02-26|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090226031456/http://www.bmi.com/news/entry/535267|archivedate=2009-02-26}}</ref> 2007年，他們於[[Lollapalooza|Lollapalooza]]音樂節表演。<ref name="seattleweekly"/>

最初，專注於[[前衛|前衛音樂]]及[[電子舞曲|電子舞曲]]。後期卡卡開始將流行音樂的旋律和[[華麗搖滾|華麗搖滾]]如大衛‧鮑伊和皇后樂團的音樂風格混合起來。在卡卡與星光持續演出時，富薩里持續與她製作音樂，並寄給{{tsl|en|music executive|唱片主管}}{{tsl|en|Vincent Herbert|樊尚·赫爾伯特}}。<ref name="trans26">{{cite video|title=Transmission Gaga-vision: Episode 26|date=2008-12-16|publisher=Lady Gaga|people=Haus of GaGa}}</ref> 2007年11月，赫爾伯特簽下了卡卡到她的品牌Streamline唱片，同時也是[[新視鏡唱片|新視鏡唱片]]的[[商業名稱|商業名稱]]，且合約當月生效。<ref name="newimprent">{{cite magazine|last=Mitchell|first=Gail|date=2007-11-10|title=Interscope's New Imprint|magazine=Billboard|volume=119|issue=45|page=14|url=https://books.google.com/?id=xw4EAAAAMBAJ&lpg=PA14|accessdate=2010-05-06|issn=0006-2510}}</ref> 卡卡在後期感謝赫爾伯特發掘她。<ref name="vincentdiscover">{{cite news|url=http://www.dailyherald.com/article/20171025/entlife/310259876|title=Singer Tamar Braxton files for divorce from husband-manager|date=2017-10-25|accessdate=2017-11-09|newspaper=[[Daily_Herald_(Arlington_Heights)|Daily Herald]]|location=Arlington|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171109134917/http://www.dailyherald.com/article/20171025/entlife/310259876|archivedate=2017-11-09}}</ref> 在著名音樂出版社擔任實習作詞人的期間，卡卡與索尼/聯合電視音樂尖下音樂出版合約。結果，她受雇為[[布蘭妮·斯皮爾斯|布蘭妮·斯皮爾斯]]、[[街頭頑童|街頭頑童]]、[[菲姬|菲姬]]，以及[[小野貓|小野貓]]等知名歌手 (團體)作曲。<ref name="bbcover">{{cite magazine|last=Harding|first=Cortney|date=2009-08-15|title=Lady Gaga: The Billboard Cover Story|magazine=Billboard|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/267810/lady-gaga-the-billboard-cover-story|accessdate=2010-05-06|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130309235202/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/267810/lady-gaga-the-billboard-cover-story|archivedate=2013-03-09}}</ref> 在新視鏡，音樂人[[阿肯|阿肯]]因卡卡在錄音室中以{{tsl|en|scratch vocal}}唱著他的歌而對卡卡感到印象深刻。<ref name="totallygaga">{{cite news|url=http://www.scotsman.com/lifestyle/lady-gaga-totally-ga-ga-1-754666|title=Lady GaGa: Totally Ga-Ga|accessdate=2009-02-20|last=Cowing|first=Emma|date=2009-01-20|work=[[The_Scotsman|The Scotsman]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208100547/http://www.scotsman.com/lifestyle/lady-gaga-totally-ga-ga-1-754666|archivedate=2015-12-08}}</ref> 阿肯說服{{tsl|en|Interscope Geffen A&M|新視鏡格芬A&M}}的董事兼執行長{{tsl|en|Jimmy Iovine|吉米·洛維恩}}，達成讓卡卡簽入自己的品牌{{tsl|en|Kon Live Distribution|Kon Live}}的聯合協議，讓卡卡成為阿肯的「特權球員」。<ref name="Allmusic bio" /><ref name="franchise">{{cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1613350/akon-calls-lady-gaga-his-franchise-player/|title=Akon Calls Lady Gaga His 'Franchise Player'|last=Vena|first=Jocelyn|date=2009-06-05|publisher=MTV News|accessdate=2009-06-20|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150204001522/http://www.mtv.com/news/1613350/akon-calls-lady-gaga-his-franchise-player/|archivedate=2015-02-04}}</ref>

2007年晚期，卡卡遇見作曲兼製作人[[RedOne|RedOne]]。<ref name="hitquarters.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.hitquarters.com/index.php3?page=intrview/opar/intrview_RedOne_Interview.html|title=Interview With RedOne|date=2009-03-23|publisher=[[HitQuarters|HitQuarters]]|accessdate=2009-12-19|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100113171226/http://www.hitquarters.com/index.php3?page=intrview%2Fopar%2Fintrview_RedOne_Interview.html|archivedate=2010-01-13|dead-url=no}}</ref> 她與他在錄音室花一個禮拜的時間製作她的首張專輯，期間卡卡與{{tsl|en|Cherrytree Records|櫻桃樹唱片}}簽下製作兼作曲人{{tsl|en|Martin Kierszenbaum|馬汀·奇阿斯邦}}的新視鏡合約書；; 她與馬汀合製了4首歌。<ref name="bbcover" /> 儘管簽下了唱片合約，卡卡表示仍有些電台認為她的音樂對主流市場來說太「活潑」，「舞曲」及「地下風」。 她聲明：「我的名字是女神卡卡，我已經在樂界打拼多年，而我要告訴你，這就是音樂的未來。」<ref name="independent">{{cite news|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/features/lady-gaga-how-the-world-went-crazy-for-the-new-queen-of-pop-1684375.html|title=Lady Gaga: How the world went crazy for the new queen of pop|last=Sturges|first=Fiona|date=2009-05-16|work=[[獨立報|The Independent]]|access-date=2009-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090519184554/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/features/lady-gaga-how-the-world-went-crazy-for-the-new-queen-of-pop-1684375.html|archive-date=2009-05-19}}</ref>

=== 2008年–2010年：以《超人气》和《超人气女魔头》取得事业突破 ===

2008年，卡卡搬遷至洛杉磯與唱片公司合作去製作她的首張專輯《[[超人氣|超人氣]]》（原文: The Fame）並參照[[安迪沃荷|安迪沃荷]]的團隊{{tsl|en|The Factory|工廠}}設立了專屬於她的藝術團隊[[Haus_of_Gaga|卡卡之屋]]。<ref name="Contactmusic.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.contactmusic.com/lady-gaga|title=Lady Gaga Biography|publisher=[[Contactmusic.com|Contactmusic.com]]|accessdate=2009-02-20|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150214150902/http://www.contactmusic.com/lady-gaga|archivedate=2015-02-14}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Inspiration|url=http://www.haus-of-gaga.com/inspiration|publisher=[[Haus_of_Gaga|Haus of Gaga]]|accessdate=2017-10-27|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171028042600/http://www.haus-of-gaga.com/inspiration|archivedate=2017-10-28}}</ref> 《超人氣》於同年8月19日發行，<ref>{{cite web|title=Lady Gaga – The Fame|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/the-fame/id1059034178|publisher=[[iTunes_Store|iTunes Store]]|accessdate=2017-08-21|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170908043311/https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/the-fame/id1059034178|archivedate=2017-09-08}}</ref> 專輯於奧地利、加拿大、德國、愛爾蘭、瑞士，以及英國排行第一，並在澳洲及美國排行前五。<ref>{{cite news|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150629212048/http://jam.canoe.com/Music/Artists/L/Lady_GaGa/2009/01/14/8022056-jam.html|archivedate=2015-06-29|url=http://jam.canoe.ca/Music/Artists/L/Lady_GaGa/2009/01/14/8022056-jam.html|title=Lady GaGa's 'Fame' rises to No. 1|work=[[Jam!|Jam!]]|first=John|last=Williams|deadurl=yes|date=2009-01-14|accessdate=2019-01-24}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://acharts.co/album/37558|title=Lady Gaga – The Fame – World Charts|publisher=aCharts.co|accessdate=2009-01-08|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151105144554/http://acharts.co/album/37558|archivedate=2015-11-05}}</ref> 專輯的前兩張單曲，《[[舞力全開_(歌曲)|舞力全開]]》(Just Dance) 和《[[撲克臉_(女神卡卡歌曲)|撲克臉]]》(Poker Face) {{sfn|Gray II|2012|p=3}} 在美國、<ref name="USsongpeaks"/> 澳洲、<ref name=Australia>{{cite web|url=http://australian-charts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Lady+GaGa|title=Discography Lady GaGa|publisher=Hung Medien|accessdate=2017-11-18|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/66tVexFYl?url=http://australian-charts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Lady+GaGa|archivedate=2012-04-13}}</ref> 加拿大，<ref name=Canada>{{cite magazine|url=http://www.billboard.com/music/Lady-Gaga/chart-history/canadian-hot-100|title=Lady Gaga Chart History: Billboard Canadian Hot 100|magazine=Billboard|accessdate=2017-11-18|archive-date=2017-11-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171102114030/http://www.billboard.com/music/lady-gaga/chart-history/canadian-hot-100|dead-url=no}}</ref> 以及英國排行第一。<ref name="ukchart"/> 其中後者更是以9.8百萬的銷量成為2009年{{tsl|en|List of best-selling singles#Best-selling single by year worldwide|世界上銷量最高的單曲}}，並在《[[告示牌_(雜誌)|告示牌]]》數位下載榜上蟬聯冠軍83周。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ifpi.org/content/library/DMR2010.pdf|title=Digital Music Sales Around The World|publisher=[[International_Federation_of_the_Phonographic_Industry|International Federation of the Phonographic Industry]]|page=10|accessdate=2017-08-04|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/66RemjMkU?url=http://www.ifpi.org/content/library/DMR2010.pdf|archivedate=2012-03-26}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Most weeks on US Hot Digital Songs chart|url=http://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/track-with-most-weeks-on-the-us-hot-digital-songs-chart|website=Guinness World Records|accessdate=2017-05-25|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924132426/http://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/track-with-most-weeks-on-the-us-hot-digital-songs-chart|archivedate=2015-09-24}}</ref> 其它三首單曲，《[[嗯，嗯（無話可說）|嗯，嗯（無話可說）]]》(Eh, Eh (Nothing Else I Can Say)) 、《[[愛情遊戲|愛情遊戲]]》(Love Game)，和《[[愛情狗仔|愛情狗仔]]》(Paparazzi) 皆在專輯發行後發行；<ref>Single releases from ''The Fame'':
* {{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.in/Eh-Nothing-Else-Can-Say/dp/B001PPLLDY|publisher=Amazon.com|accessdate=2017-11-17|title=Eh Eh (Nothing Else I Can Say) Single|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171119070403/https://www.amazon.in/Eh-Nothing-Else-Can-Say/dp/B001PPLLDY|archivedate=2017-11-19}}
* {{cite web|url=http://www.capitalfm.com/photos/music-photos/fans-super-seven/lady-gaga-1/|title=No 7: Love Game|accessdate=2017-11-17|publisher=Capital FM|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171119070403/http://www.capitalfm.com/photos/music-photos/fans-super-seven/lady-gaga-1/|archivedate=2017-11-19}}
* {{cite magazine|url=http://www.harpersbazaar.com/culture/art-books-music/news/a20208/lady-gaga-best-live-performances/|magazine=Harper's Bazaar|title=Lady Gaga's 10 Most Amazing Live Performances|first=Morgan|last=Evans|date=2017-01-31|accessdate=2017-11-17|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170203212846/http://www.harpersbazaar.com/culture/art-books-music/news/a20208/lady-gaga-best-live-performances/|archivedate=2017-02-03}}</ref> 其中《愛情狗仔》於德國排行第一。<ref name="Germany">{{cite web|url=http://www.musicline.de/de/chartverfolgung_summary/artist/Lady+Gaga/14039/single|title=Chartverfolgung / Lady Gaga / Single|publisher=[[GfK_Entertainment|GfK Entertainment]]|language=de|accessdate=2011-03-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131102170723/http://www.musicline.de/de/chartverfolgung_summary/artist/Lady%2BGaga/14039/single|archivedate=2013-11-02}}</ref> 2009年8月，除了《嗯，嗯（無話可說）》，其它單曲的再編曲版皆收錄於迷你專輯《[[Hitmixes|Hitmixes]]》。<ref>{{cite web|title=Hit Mixes – Lady Gaga|url=https://www.allmusic.com/album/hit-mixes-mw0000825184|publisher=AllMusic|accessdate=2017-11-07|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107222336/https://www.allmusic.com/album/hit-mixes-mw0000825184|archivedate=2017-11-07}}</ref> 在[[第52屆葛萊美獎|第52屆葛萊美獎]]中，《超人氣》與《撲克臉》分別贏得了最佳電音/舞曲專輯以及最佳舞曲錄製。.<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2010/SHOWBIZ/Music/01/31/grammys.winner.list/index.html|title=List of Grammy winners|publisher=CNN|date=2010-02-01|accessdate=2010-04-25|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100419055243/http://www.cnn.com/2010/SHOWBIZ/Music/01/31/grammys.winner.list/index.html|archivedate=2010-04-19}}</ref>

