自卡卡2009年於[[小野貓|小野貓]]範圍遍及歐洲和大洋洲的巡演{{link-en|我最大巡迴演出|Doll Domination Tour}}中擔任開場嘉賓後，卡卡於同年3月開始了由她主持的{{tsl|en|The Fame Ball Tour|超人氣巡迴演唱會}}並結束至9月。{{sfn|Morgan|2010|p=131}} 在巡迴世界的同時，她為了專輯的再版《[[超人氣魔神|超人氣魔神]]》（原文: The Fame Monster）錄製了8首歌。<ref>{{cite press release|url=http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/lady-gaga-returns-with-8-new-songs-on-the-fame-monster-63780227.html|title=Lady Gaga Returns With 8 New Songs on 'The Fame Monster'|date=2009-10-08|agency=[[PR_Newswire|PR Newswire]]|accessdate=2009-10-09|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20091011005910/http://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/lady-gaga-returns-with-8-new-songs-on-the-fame-monster-63780227.html|archivedate=2009-10-11}}</ref> 這些歌曲最後以獨立[[迷你專輯|迷你專輯]]的形式於11月19日發行。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.slantmagazine.com/music/review/lady-gaga-the-fame-monster|work=Slant Magazine|title=Lady Gaga The Fame Monster|date=2009-11-18|accessdate=2017-10-29|first=Sal|last=Cinquemani|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171009050132/https://www.slantmagazine.com/music/review/lady-gaga-the-fame-monster|archivedate=2017-10-09}}</ref> 專輯首單，《[[羅曼死|羅曼死]]》(Bad Romance) 於專輯發行前一個月釋出<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.axs.com/news/lady-gaga-becomes-first-woman-to-earn-digital-diamond-award-for-bad-ro-10969|publisher=AXS|date=2014-05-16|accessdate=2017-10-29|first=Lucas|last=Villa|title=Lady Gaga becomes first woman to earn Digital Diamond Award for 'Bad Romance'|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171030003236/https://www.axs.com/news/lady-gaga-becomes-first-woman-to-earn-digital-diamond-award-for-bad-ro-10969|archivedate=2017-10-30}}</ref> 並於加拿大<ref name=Canada/> 及英國排行第1，<ref name="ukchart"/> 於美國、<ref name="USsongpeaks"/> 澳洲、<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Lady+Gaga&titel=Bad+Romance&cat=s|title=Australian-charts.com – Lady Gaga – Bad Romance|accessdate=2017-10-29|publisher=Hung Medien|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171030003538/http://www.australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Lady+Gaga&titel=Bad+Romance&cat=s|archivedate=2017-10-30}}</ref> 和紐西蘭排行第2。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.charts.org.nz/showitem.asp?interpret=Lady+Gaga&titel=Bad+Romance&cat=s|title=Charts.org.nz – Lady Gaga – Bad Romance|accessdate=2017-10-29|publisher=Hung Medien|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171030005104/http://www.charts.org.nz/showitem.asp?interpret=Lady+Gaga&titel=Bad+Romance&cat=s|archivedate=2017-10-30}}</ref> 與女歌手[[碧昂絲|碧昂絲]]合作的歌曲《[[電話_(歌曲)|電話]]》(Telephone) 作為迷你專輯的第二張單曲成為了卡卡在英國的第四張冠軍單曲。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Daw|first1=Robbie|title=Lady Gaga-Beyonce Duet 'Telephone' Set As Next 'Fame Monster' Single|url=https://www.idolator.com/5294222/lady-gagas-beyonce-duet-telephone-set-to-be-the-next-single|publisher=Idolator|date=2009-11-12|accessdate=2017-11-17|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131102231004/http://www.idolator.com/5294222/lady-gagas-beyonce-duet-telephone-set-to-be-the-next-single|archivedate=2013-11-02}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Lady Gaga tops UK album and single charts|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/8579244.stm|work=BBC News|date=2010-03-22|accessdate=2010-12-13|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100819052041/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/8579244.stm|archivedate=2010-08-19}}</ref> 第三張單曲《[[亞歷山卓_(歌曲)|亞歷山卓]]》(Alejandro) <ref>{{cite news|title=Lady Gaga releases 'Alejandro' remix album|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/lady-gaga-releases-alejandro-remix-album-5541933.html|accessdate=2017-11-17|work=The Independent|date=2010-05-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171119070403/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/lady-gaga-releases-alejandro-remix-album-5541933.html|archivedate=2017-11-19}}</ref> 於芬蘭排行第一<ref>{{cite web|title=Lady Gaga – Alejandro (song)|url=http://www.ultratop.be/en/showitem.asp?interpret=Lady+GaGa&titel=Alejandro&cat=s|archivedate=2012-04-21|publisher=Hung Medien|accessdate=2017-11-17|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/67674zLZs?url=http://www.ultratop.be/en/showitem.asp?interpret=Lady+GaGa}}</ref> 且歌曲的音樂影片吸引了{{tsl|en|Catholic League (U.S.)|全美天主教聯盟}}的注意並批評影片內容是在[[褻瀆|褻瀆]]上帝。<ref>{{cite web|title=Lady Gaga Mimics Madonna|url=http://www.catholicleague.org/lady-gaga-mimics-madonna/|work=[[Catholic_League_(U.S.)|Catholic League]]|accessdate=2017-10-27|date=2010-06-09|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170630021632/http://www.catholicleague.org/lady-gaga-mimics-madonna/|archivedate=2017-06-30}}</ref> 上述兩張單曲皆於美國排行第5。<ref name="USsongpeaks"/> 2012年4月，《羅曼死》的音樂影片成為了[[Youtube|Youtube]][[觀看次數最多的YouTube影片列表|觀看次數最多的影片]]，而同年十月，卡卡成為了第一名擁有影片合計達十億觀看次數的人。<ref>{{cite magazine|last1=O'Neill|first1=Megan|title=Lady Gaga's Bad Romance Is Officially The Most Viewed Video On YouTube Ever|url=http://www.adweek.com/digital/lady-gaga%E2%80%99s-bad-romance-is-officially-the-most-viewed-video-on-youtube-ever/|accessdate=2017-05-14|magazine=[[Adweek|Adweek]]|date=2010-04-14|archive-date=2017-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170514111237/http://www.adweek.com/digital/lady-gaga%E2%80%99s-bad-romance-is-officially-the-most-viewed-video-on-youtube-ever/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/article/11626592/lady-gaga-beats-justin-bieber-to-youtube-record|title=Lady Gaga beats Justin Bieber to YouTube record|last=Whitworth|first=Dan|date=2010-10-26|work=BBC News|accessdate=2010-12-28|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151105144824/http://www.bbc.co.uk/newsbeat/article/11626592/lady-gaga-beats-justin-bieber-to-youtube-record|archivedate=2015-11-05}}</ref> 在[[2010年MTV音樂錄影帶大獎|2010年MTV音樂錄影帶大獎]]時，卡卡在13項提名中獲獎8項，其中包含了《羅曼死》的{{tsl|en|MTV Video Music Award for Video of the Year|年度最佳音樂錄影帶}}。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/ontv/vma/2010/|title=MTV Video Music Awards 2010|publisher=MTV|date=2010-09-12|accessdate=2012-01-30|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150205094153/http://www.mtv.com/ontv/vma/2010/|archivedate=2015-02-05}}</ref> 她成為了當屆獲得最多提名的女歌手，同時也是首位在年度最佳音樂錄影帶中獲兩次提名的女性<ref>{{cite web|last1=Kaufman|first1=Gil|title=Lady Gaga's 13 VMA Nominations: How Do They Measure Up?|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1644983/lady-gagas-13-vma-nominations-how-do-they-measure-up/|publisher=MTV News|accessdate=2016-12-16|date=2010-08-03|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170510064405/http://www.mtv.com/news/1644983/lady-gagas-13-vma-nominations-how-do-they-measure-up/|archivedate=2017-05-10}}</ref> 《[[超人氣魔神|超人氣魔神]]》贏得了葛萊美獎{{tsl|en|Grammy Award for Best Pop Vocal Album|最佳流行演唱專輯}}，而《羅曼死》則贏得了{{tsl|en|Grammy Award for Best Female Pop Vocal Performance|最佳流行女歌手}}以及{{tsl|en|Grammy Award for Best Short Form Music Video|最佳短篇音樂錄影帶}}。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://marquee.blogs.cnn.com/2011/02/13/53rd-annual-grammy-awards-the-winners-list/|title=53rd annual Grammy awards: The winners list|publisher=CNN|accessdate=2011-07-17|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110708172128/http://marquee.blogs.cnn.com/2011/02/13/53rd-annual-grammy-awards-the-winners-list/|archivedate=2011-07-08}}</ref>


2009年，卡卡在[[英國單曲排行榜|英國單曲排行榜]]上停留150周成為了年度美國作品最多下載次數的女歌手，且同時以1.11億的下載次數登上《[[金氏世界紀錄|金氏世界紀錄]]》。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/most-cumulative-weeks-on-uk-singles-chart-in-one-year|title=Most cumulative weeks on UK singles chart in one year|work=[[Guinness_World_Records|Guinness World Records]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924130850/http://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/most-cumulative-weeks-on-uk-singles-chart-in-one-year|archivedate=2015-09-24|accessdate=2017-11-07}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/most-downloaded-act-in-a-year-(usa)-female/|title=Most downloaded act in a year (USA) – female|work=Guinness World Records|accessdate=2017-05-25|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170714204817/http://www.guinnessworldrecords.com/world-records/most-downloaded-act-in-a-year-%28usa%29-female/|archivedate=2017-07-14}}</ref> 《超人氣》與《超人氣魔神》總和於全球的銷售量超過了1.5億。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.asiaone.com/print/News/Latest%2BNews/Showbiz/Story/A1Story20120227-330396.html|title=Lady Gaga adds second show in Singapore|publisher=[[AsiaOne|AsiaOne]]|date=2012-02-27|accessdate=2017-12-04|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171204222917/http://www.asiaone.com/print/News/Latest%2BNews/Showbiz/Story/A1Story20120227-330396.html|archivedate=2017-12-04}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://blog.thenewstribune.com/getout/2012/09/18/lady-gaga-fills-in-the-details-on-her-tacoma-show/|title=Lady Gaga fills in the details on her Tacoma show|work=[[The_News_Tribune|The News Tribune]]|first=Craig|last=Sailor|date=2012-09-18|accessdate=2017-12-04|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171204222958/http://blog.thenewstribune.com/getout/2012/09/18/lady-gaga-fills-in-the-details-on-her-tacoma-show/|archivedate=2017-12-04}}</ref> 這樣的成功促使公司同意卡卡開始她的第二場巡演{{link-en|魔神巡迴演唱會|The Monster Ball Tour}}，並發行了她最後一張與櫻桃樹唱片錄製的，她{{tsl|en|List of best-selling remix albums|有史以來最暢銷的混音專輯}}《{{tsl|en|The Remix (Lady Gaga album)|The remix}}》。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://articles.latimes.com/2011/jun/29/entertainment/la-et-martin-kierszenbaum-20110629|title=Martin Kierszenbaum has a knack for finding the next big thing|last=Newman|first=Melinda|date=2011-06-29|work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131029223357/http://articles.latimes.com/2011/jun/29/entertainment/la-et-martin-kierszenbaum-20110629|archivedate=2013-10-29|deadurl=no|accessdate=2013-02-13}}</ref> <ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1643274/20100708/lady_gaga.jhtml|title=Lady Gaga Remix Album Due In The U.S. Next Month|last=Ziegbe|first=Mawuse|date=2010-07-08|accessdate=2016-12-17|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101208061002/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1643274/20100708/lady_gaga.jhtml|archivedate=2010-12-08|deadurl=no|publisher=MTV News}}</ref><ref name="bbannounceball">{{cite magazine|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/267048/lady-gaga-unveils-monster-ball-tour-dates-the-fame-monster-tracklist|title=Lady Gaga Unveils 'The Monster Ball'|accessdate=2009-10-15|date=2009-10-15|last=Herrera|first=Monica|magazine=Billboard|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160223023430/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/267048/lady-gaga-unveils-monster-ball-tour-dates-the-fame-monster-tracklist|archivedate=2016-02-23}}</ref> 魔神巡迴演唱會從2009年11月巡演至2011年5月並賺了2.274億美元，成為了{{tsl|en|List of highest-grossing concert tours|首次登台的藝術家收入最高的演唱會}}。<ref name="guardian">{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/musicblog/2009/nov/30/lady-gaga-monster-ball|title=Lady Gaga's Monster Ball, reviewed by a theatre critic|last=Nestruck|first=Kelly|date=2009-11-30|newspaper=The Guardian|accessdate=2009-12-01|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304024732/http://www.theguardian.com/music/musicblog/2009/nov/30/lady-gaga-monster-ball|archivedate=2016-03-04}}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/photos/live/471708/lady-gagas-monster-ball-tour-breaks-record-for-debut-headlining-artist|title=Lady Gaga's Monster Ball Tour Breaks Record for Debut Headlining Artist|date=2011-05-05|first=Ray|last=Waddell|magazine=Billboard|accessdate=2011-06-02|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130509041933/http://www.billboard.com/articles/photos/live/471708/lady-gagas-monster-ball-tour-breaks-record-for-debut-headlining-artist|archivedate=2013-05-09}}</ref> 其中巡演場次之一，位於紐約市的[[麥迪遜廣場花園|麥迪遜廣場花園]]演唱會由[[HBO|HBO]]轉播為電視特別節目《{{tsl|en|Lady Gaga Presents the Monster Ball Tour: At Madison Square Garden|女神卡卡魔神巡迴演唱會 : 麥迪遜廣場花園}}》。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.emmys.com/shows/lady-gaga-presents-monster-ball-tour-madison-square-garden|title=Lady GaGa Presents The Monster Ball Tour: At Madison Square Garden|publisher=[[Academy_of_Television_Arts_&_Sciences|Academy of Television Arts & Sciences]]|accessdate=2011-08-25|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150110192149/http://www.emmys.com/shows/lady-gaga-presents-monster-ball-tour-madison-square-garden|archivedate=2015-01-10}}</ref> 卡卡同時也於2009年[[皇家大匯演|皇家大匯演]]、第52界葛萊美，以及{{tsl|en|2010 BRIT Awards|2010年全英音樂獎}}中表演專輯的歌曲。<ref>{{cite news|title=Lady Gaga wins Brit Awards triple|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/8517579.stm|work=BBC News|date=2010-02-16|accessdate=2010-12-28|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101013070214/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/8517579.stm|archivedate=2010-10-13}}<br>{{cite web|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/theroyalfamily/6756304/Lady-Gaga-meets-the-Queen-at-the-Royal-Variety-Performance-in-Blackpool.html|title=Lady Gaga meets the Queen at the Royal Variety Performance in Blackpool|work=The Daily Telegraph|accessdate=2017-10-27|date=2009-12-07|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161007085711/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/uknews/theroyalfamily/6756304/Lady-Gaga-meets-the-Queen-at-the-Royal-Variety-Performance-in-Blackpool.html|archivedate=2016-10-07}}<br>{{cite web|url=http://www.newnownext.com/lady-gagas-10-best-live-performances/11/2013/|title=Lady Gaga's 10 Best Live Performances|publisher=[[Logo_TV|Logo TV]]|date=2013-11-12|first=Louis|last=Virtel|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160313031648/http://www.newnownext.com/lady-gagas-10-best-live-performances/11/2013/|archivedate=2016-03-13|accessdate=2017-11-07}}</ref> 甚至在[[麥克·傑克森|麥克·傑克森]]逝世前，卡卡原定將於英國倫敦[[O2體育館|O<sub>2</sub>體育館]]的[[This_Is_It_(迈克尔·杰克逊演唱会)|This Is It謝幕演唱會]]表演中登台客串。<ref>{{cite magazine|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/viral-videos/957954/lady-gaga-talks-michael-jackson-lupus-diagnosis-with-larry-king|title=Lady Gaga Talks Michael Jackson, Lupus Diagnosis with Larry King|date=2010-06-01|accessdate=2011-05-30|first=Monica|last=Herrera|magazine=Billboard|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130509040237/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/viral-videos/957954/lady-gaga-talks-michael-jackson-lupus-diagnosis-with-larry-king|archivedate=2013-05-09}}</ref>

