=== 2011年–2014年：《天生完美》、《流行艺术》及《脸贴脸》 ===

2011年2月，卡卡發行專輯《[[天生完美|天生完美]]》（原文: Born This Way）的[[天生完美_(歌曲)|同名單曲]]，單曲在發行五天內銷量超過百萬，並在《[[金氏世界紀錄|金氏世界紀錄]]》獲稱為「[[iTunes|iTunes]]銷量速度最快的單曲」。<ref name="champ">{{cite web|date=2011-05-18|url=http://www.livescience.com/33288-lady-gagas-world-records.html/|title=The Lady Is a Champ: Lady Gaga Sets Twitter Record|work=[[LiveScience|LiveScience]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130702233957/http://www.livescience.com/33288-lady-gagas-world-records.html|archivedate=2013-07-02|accessdate=2020-01-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>  單曲於《[[告示牌百大單曲榜|告示牌百大單曲榜]]》中{{tsl|en|List of Billboard Hot 100 chart achievements and milestones#Number-one debuts|排行第一}}，並成為了該榜史上第一千首冠軍單曲。<ref>{{cite magazine|last=Trust|first=Gary|title=Lady Gaga Claims 1,000th Hot 100 No. 1 with 'Born This Way'|magazine=Billboard|date=2011-02-16|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/473025/lady-gaga-claims-1000th-hot-100-no-1-with-born-this-way|accessdate=2011-02-16|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130325075536/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/473025/lady-gaga-claims-1000th-hot-100-no-1-with-born-this-way|archivedate=2013-03-25}}</ref> 兩個月後，專輯第二首單曲《[[猶大_(女神卡卡歌曲)|猶大]]》(Judas) 發行，<ref name="dwn">{{cite news|url=http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/music_blog/2011/04/lady-gaga-judas-single.html|title=New Lady Gaga single 'Judas' released today|work=Los Angeles Times|first=Randy|last=Lewis|date=2011-04-15|accessdate=2011-04-16|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110418233534/http://latimesblogs.latimes.com/music_blog/2011/04/lady-gaga-judas-single.html|archivedate=2011-04-18}}</ref> 而《[[幸福邊界|幸福邊界]]》(The Edge of Glory) 則做為第三首單曲於後發行。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.digitalspy.com/music/news/a318892/lady-gaga-makes-edge-of-glory-official-single/|title=Lady Gaga Makes Edge Of Glory Official Single?|last=Corner|first=Nick|date=2011-05-11|accessdate=2011-10-29|work=[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151212062409/http://www.digitalspy.com/music/n