13名。<ref name="USsongpeaks" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://zene.slagerlistak.hu/single-track-top-40-lista/2013/43|title=2013/43. heti Single (track) Top 40 lista|publisher=Slágerlisták|language=hu|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171030094255/http://zene.slagerlistak.hu/single-track-top-40-lista/2013/43|archivedate=2017-10-30|deadurl=no|accessdate=2017-10-29}}</ref> 《流行藝術》於同年11月發行，並獲得了「褒貶不一」的總評價。<ref>{{cite web|title=Reviews for ARTPOP by Lady Gaga|url=http://www.metacritic.com/music/artpop/lady-gaga|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|accessdate=2013-11-30|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408010610/http://www.metacritic.com/music/artpop/lady-gaga|archivedate=2014-04-08}}</ref> 《每日電訊報》的海倫·布朗恩起初批評卡卡只做了另一張以「名氣」為主題的專輯並懷疑專輯的原創性，但隨後讚美《流行藝術》有著「很好的舞動性」<ref name="telegraph">{{cite news|last=Brown|first=Helen|title=Lady Gaga, Artpop, review|url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/cdreviews/10432368/Lady-Gaga-Artpop-review.html|accessdate=2013-11-08|work=The Daily Telegraph|date=2013-11-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131111114033/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/cdreviews/10432368/Lady-Gaga-Artpop-review.html|archivedate=2013-11-11|deadurl=no}}</ref> 隔年7月，專輯憑著全球銷量2.5百萬份的成績登上《告示牌兩百大專輯榜》冠軍。<ref>{{cite magazine|last=Caulfield|first=Keith|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5793353/lady-gaga-scores-second-no-1-album-with-artpop|title=Lady Gaga Scores Second No. 1 Album With 'ARTPOP'|magazine=Billboard|date=2013-11-20|accessdate=2013-11-20|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140126054832/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/5793353/lady-gaga-scores-second-no-1-album-with-artpop|archivedate=2014-01-26}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Lady Gaga dazzles fans with fun, solid show|url=http://www.buffalonews.com/gusto/concert-reviews/lady-gaga-dazzles-fans-with-fun-solid-show-20140707|work=[[The_Buffalo_News|The Buffalo News]]|accessdate=2016-02-26|date=2014-07-07|last=Siegel|first=Ben|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140710005135/http://www.buffalonews.com/gusto/concert-reviews/lady-gaga-dazzles-fans-with-fun-solid-show-20140707|archivedate=2014-07-10}}</ref> 《男子漢》(G.U.Y.) 做為第三首單曲於3月釋出並於美國榜單排行第76名。<ref name="USsongpeaks" /><ref name="radioit">{{cite web|url=http://www.radioairplay.fm/RadioDate/PublicDetails/61964|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141028104145/http://www.radioairplay.fm/RadioDate/PublicDetails/61964|archivedate=2014-10-28|title=G.U.Y.: Lady Gaga|last=Mompellio|first=Gabriel|date=2014-03-28|publisher=Radio Airplay Italy|language=it|accessdate=2017-11-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref>
