ga-brings-over-the-top-style-roseland-final-shows-article-1.1738728|title=Lady Gaga brings signature over-the-top style, familiar hits to Roseland Ballroom's final shows|first=Jim|last=Farber|newspaper=Daily News|location=New York|date=2014-03-29|accessdate=2017-10-29|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170711013553/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/music-arts/lady-gaga-brings-over-the-top-style-roseland-final-shows-article-1.1738728|archivedate=2017-07-11}}</ref> 兩個月後，卡卡開始了[[流行藝術巡迴演唱會|藝術狂歡:流行藝術巡迴演唱會]]的巡演，演唱會的概念源自於專輯宣傳活動之一的{{tsl|en|ArtRave|藝術狂歡}}。巡演總收入為8.3千萬美元，其中巡演的場次包含了先前天生完美狂歡派對中取消的場次。<ref>{{cite magazine|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6363749/rolling-stones-lady-gaga-wrap-up-tours-on-top|title=Rolling Stones & Lady Gaga Wrap Up Their Tours on Top|last=Allen|first=Bob|date=2014-12-05|magazine=Billboard|accessdate=2014-12-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150318033529/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/6363749/rolling-stones-lady-gaga-wrap-up-tours-on-top|archivedate=2015-03-18|deadurl=no}}</ref> 與此同時，卡卡與她同行多年的經紀人{{tsl|en|Troy Carter (music industry)|特洛伊‧卡特}}因創意理念不合而決裂，<ref name="NY news">{{cite news|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/music-arts/lady-gaga-longtime-manager-troy-carter-split-article-1.1507097|title=Lady Gaga, longtime manager Troy Carter split over 'creative differences': report|author=Rivera, Zayda|date=2013-11-05|newspaper=Daily News|location=New York|accessdate=2013-11-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131107040822/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/music-arts/lady-gaga-longtime-manager-troy-carter-split-article-1.1507097|archivedate=2013-11-07|deadurl=no}}</ref> 2014年6月時，她的新經紀人巴比·坎貝爾跳槽到娛樂公司[[Live_Nation_Entertainment|Live Nation Entertainment]]的藝術管理部門—Artist Nation。<ref name="tourforce">{{cite magazine|url=https://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/news/legal-and-management/6114193/lady-gaga-and-manager-bobby-campbell-join-artist|title=Lady Gaga and Manager Bobby Campbell Join Artist Nation (Exclusive)|last=Waddell|first=Ray|magazine=Billboard|date=2014-06-11|access-date=2014-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140614153159/http://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/news/legal-and-management/6114193/lady-gaga-and-manager-bobby-campbell-join-artist|archive-date=2014-06-14}}</ref> 這期間，她曾以配角的身分短暫出現在[[勞勃·羅瑞格茲|勞勃·羅瑞格茲]]的電影《[[萬惡城市2：紅顏奪命|萬惡城市2：紅顏奪命]]》，並同時確認將出席時尚品牌[[范思哲|凡賽斯]]的春夏活動《Lady Gaga For Versace》。<ref name=GagaNailedIt>{{cite news|last=Vena|first=Jocelyn|title=Lady Gaga 'Nailed It' In 'Sin City' Sequel, Joseph Gordon-Levitt Reveals|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1713289/lady-gaga-joseph-gordon-levitt-sin-city-2/|publisher=MTV News|accessdate=2013-08-29|date=2013-08-29|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140523195125/http://www.mtv.com/news/1713289/lady-gaga-joseph-gordon-levitt-sin-city-2/|archivedate=2014-05-23}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Lady Gaga for Versace confirmed|work=The Daily Telegraph|url=http://fashion.telegraph.co.uk/article/TMG10472239/Gaga-for-Versace-confirmed.html|date=2013-11-25|accessdate=2015-06-17|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150617082141/http://fashion.telegraph.co.uk/article/TMG10472239/Gaga-for-Versace-confirmed.html|archivedate=2015-06-17}}</ref>

2014年9月，卡卡發行了與東尼·班奈特合作的爵士樂專輯《[[爵對經典|爵對經典]]》（原文: Cheek To Cheek）。專輯靈感起於她與班奈特的友誼，以及她童年時期時[[爵士樂|爵士]]對她散發的魅力。<ref name="press">{{cite press release|url=http://www.universalmusic.ca/press-releases/tony-bennett-lady-gaga-cheek-to-cheek-album-of-classic-jazz-standards-to-be-released-september-23/|title=Tony Bennett & Lady Gaga: ''Cheek to Cheek'' Album of Classic Jazz Standards To Be Released September 23|date=2014-07-29|accessdate=2014-07-30|publisher=[[Universal_Music_Canada|Universal Music Canada]]|location=Toronto|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140808051628/http://www.universalmusic.ca/press-releases/tony-bennett-lady-gaga-cheek-to-cheek-album-of-classic-jazz-standards-to-be-released-september-23/|archivedate=2014-08-08}}</ref> 在專輯發行前，就已先發行單曲《{{tsl|en|Anything Goes (Cole Porter song)#Tony Bennett and Lady Gaga version|萬事皆空}}》(Anything Goes) 以及《{{tsl|en|I Can't Give You Anything but Love, Baby#Tony Bennett and Lady Gaga version|無法給你一切，除了愛}}》(I Can't Give You Anything but Love) 。<ref>{{cite magazine|url=http://time.com/3143169/lady-gaga-tony-bennett-cheek-to-cheek/|title=Lady Gaga Unveils Cover Art For Duet Album With Tony Bennett|last=Gibson|first=Megan|date=2014-08-19|accessdate=2017-11-07|magazine=Time|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160609195158/http://time.com/3143169/lady-gaga-tony-bennett-cheek-to-cheek/|archivedate=2016-06-09}}</ref> 《爵對經典》獲得的總評價為「普遍好評」:<ref name="mc">{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/music/cheek-to-cheek/tony-bennett|title=Cheek to Cheek – Tony Bennett and Lady Gaga|accessdate=2014-10-18|publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140927063411/http://www.metacritic.com/music/cheek-to-cheek/tony-bennett|archivedate=2014-09-27}}</ref> 《[[衛報|衛報]]》的卡蘿琳·蘇利文讚美卡卡的聲線，而《芝加哥論壇報》的豪沃德·萊克則在專欄中寫下「《爵對經典》從開頭到結尾，為聽眾提供了真實的事物。」。<ref name="guarrev">{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/music/2014/sep/18/tony-bennett-and-lady-gaga-review-gaga-is-a-wonder|date=2014-09-18|accessdate=2014-09-18|newspaper=The Guardian|first=Caroline|last=Sullivan|title=Tony Bennett & Lady Gaga review – Gaga is a wonder|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140919072138/http://www.theguardian.com/music/2014/sep/18/tony-bennett-and-lady-gaga-review-gaga-is-a-wonder|archivedate=2014-09-19}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last1=Reich|first1=Howard|title=Lady Gaga and Tony Bennett meet 'Cheek to Cheek'|url=http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/music/reich/ct-lady-gaga-tony-bennett-gaga-cheek-to-cheek-20140919-column.html|accessdate=2014-09-19|work=Chicago Tribune|date=2014-09-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140920084719/http://www.chicagotribune.com/entertainment/music/reich/ct-lady-gaga-tony-bennett-gaga-cheek-to-cheek-20140919-column.html|archivedate=2014-09-20}}</ref> 該專輯是卡卡連續第三張《告示牌兩百大專輯榜》的冠軍專輯，<ref name="usc2c">{{cite magazine|url=http://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/6266770/tony-bennett-lady-gagas-cheek-to-cheek-debuts-at-no-1|title=Tony Bennett & Lady Gaga's 'Cheek To Cheek' Debuts at No. 1|last=Caulfield|first=Keith|date=2014-10-01|accessdate=2014-10-01|magazine=Billboard|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141003135447/http://www.billboard.com/biz/articles/6266770/tony-bennett-lady-gagas-cheek-to-cheek-debuts-at-no-1|archivedate=2014-10-03}}</ref> 並贏得了葛萊美獎{{tsl|en|Grammy Award for Best Traditional Pop Vocal Album|最佳傳統流行演唱專輯}}。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/02/08/grammy-winners-list-2015_n_6600948.html|title=Grammy Winners List For 2015 Includes Beyoncé, 'Frozen' & Kendrick Lamar|last=Rosen|first=Christopher|date=2015-02-08|accessdate=2015-02-08|work=HuffPost|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150209033006/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/02/08/grammy-winners-list-2015_n_6600948.html|archivedate=2015-02-09}}</ref> 兩人也合作錄製了演唱會錄影片《{{tsl|en|Tony Bennett and Lady Gaga: Cheek to Cheek Live!|東尼·班奈特與女神卡卡: 爵對經典Live!}}》，<ref>{{cite news|title=Tony Bennett & Lady Ga