2015年，女神卡卡與男演員[[泰勒·金尼|泰勒·金尼]]訂婚。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Lewis|first1=Barry|title=Our editor congratulated her: Lady Gaga is engaged|url=http://www.recordonline.com/article/20150216/ENTERTAINMENT/150219500|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151015101315/http://www.recordonline.com/article/20150216/ENTERTAINMENT/150219500|archivedate=2015-10-15|deadurl=no|work=[[Times-Herald_Record|Times-Herald Record]]|date=2015-02-16|accessdate=2017-11-07}}</ref>

自第三張專輯《[[流行藝術|流行藝術]]》（原文: ARTPOP）獲得「褒貶不一」的評價後，女神卡卡開始重新塑造她的形象及造型。根據音樂雜誌《[[告示牌_(雜誌)|告示牌]]》的說法，該一轉變始於爵士樂專輯《[[爵對經典|爵對經典]]》（原文: Cheek To Cheek）以及她於[[第87屆奧斯卡金像獎|第87屆奧斯卡金像獎]]的表演所受到的關注，她表演中演唱了《[[真善美_(電影)|真善美]]》的歌曲，並同時向[[茱莉·安德魯絲|茱莉·安德魯絲]]致敬。<ref name="reinvention">{{cite magazine |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/business/6494560/inside-lady-gaga-reinvention-long-term-plan |title=Inside Lady Gaga's Latest Reinvention (It's All Part of a Long-Term Plan) |date=2015-03-06 |magazine=Billboard |accessdate=2016-02-28 |author=Hampp, Andrew |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308080718/http://www.billboard.com/articles/business/6494560/inside-lady-gaga-reinvention-long-term-plan |archivedate=2016-03-08 }}</ref> 該場表演被《[[告示牌_(雜誌)|告示牌]]》認證為她最棒的幾場表演之一，並在全球[[臉書|臉書]]中引發了每分鐘超過214,000次的轉發。<ref>{{cite magazine |last1=Stecker |first1=Erin |title=Lady Gaga's 8 Best Live Performances |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6259156/lady-gagas-7-best-live-performances |accessdate=2017-11-07 |magazine=Billboard |date=2016-02-08 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160313175522/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6259156/lady-gagas-7-best-live-performances |archivedate=2016-03-13 }}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscars-2015-social-media-lady-777016 |title=Oscars 2015: Lady Gaga's 'The Sound of Music' Medley Dominated Social Media |first=Ashley |last=Lee |date=2015-02-23 |magazine=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |accessdate=2015-07-11 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160320064321/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscars-2015-social-media-lady-777016 |archivedate=2016-03-20 }}</ref> 她和作詞家黛安·沃倫為紀錄片《狩獵場》合寫歌曲《直到你身歷其境》(Til It Happens to You) ，該曲於 2016年獲得[[第20屆衛星獎|第20屆衛星獎]]的最佳原創歌曲並同時於[[第88屆奧斯卡金像獎|第88屆奧斯卡獎]]中受提名最佳原創歌曲。<ref>{{cite magazine|last=Gallo|first=Phil|title=Diane Warren on Her Lady Gaga Collaboration for New Documentary 'The Hunting Ground'|magazine=Billboard|date=2015-01-27|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6451064/diane-warren-lady-gaga-song-till-it-happens-to-you-hunting-ground|accessdate=2015-05-04|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150428095535/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6451064/diane-warren-lady-gaga-song-till-it-happens-to-you-hunting-ground|archivedate=2015-04-28}}<br />{{cite web |url=http://www.pressacademy.com/award_cat/2015/ |title=View Awards by Year: 2015 |publisher=International Press Academy |accessdate=2015-12-05 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160320045213/http://www.pressacademy.com/award_cat/2015/ |archivedate=2016-03-20 }}<br />{{cite news |url=http://www.cnn.com/2016/02/28/entertainment/oscars-2016-winners-list-feat/index.html |title=The 2016 Oscars winners list |first=Katia |last=Hetter |date=2016-02-28 |accessdate=2016-02-28 |publisher=CNN |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160229020329/http://www.cnn.com/2016/02/28/entertainment/oscars-2016-winners-list-feat/index.html |archivedate=2016-02-29 }}</ref> 2015年，卡卡獲得了《告示牌》「年度女性獎」以及在2015年度作曲名人堂中獲得「當代偶像獎」。<ref name="2015bbwoman">{{cite magazine |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6714424/billboard-lady-gaga-woman-of-the-year-women-in-music-lifetime-2015 |title=Lady Gaga to Be Honored as Billboard's 2015 Woman of the Year, Lifetime to Televise Annual Event |last=Sun |first=Rebecca |date=2015-09-30 |magazine=Billboard |accessdate=2015-09-30 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151002010117/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6714424/billboard-lady-gaga-woman-of-the-year-women-in-music-lifetime-2015 |archivedate=2015-10-02 }}</ref><ref name="iconaward">{{cite web |url=http://www.songhall.org/news/entry/lady_gaga_to_receive_first_ever_contemporary_icon_award |title=Lady Gaga To Receive First-Ever Contemporary Icon Award |date=2015-04-23 |publisher=[[Songwriters_Hall_of_Fame|Songwriters Hall of Fame]] |accessdate=2015-04-24 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150505045400/http://www.songhall.org/news/entry/lady_gaga_to_receive_first_ever_contemporary_icon_award |archivedate=2015-05-05 }}</ref>

卡卡曾表示她早年一直想成為一名女演員，並在自己接獲主演《[[美國恐怖故事：旅館|美國恐怖故事：旅館]]》時，她相信自己實現了自己的目標。<ref name=GoldenGlobeAHS>{{cite magazine |last1=David |first1=Ehrlich |title=Watch Lady Gaga's Emotional Speech at 2016 Golden Globes |url=https://www.rollingstone.com/tv/news/lady-gaga-i-wanted-to-be-an-actress-before-a-singer-20160110 |accessdate=2017-05-22 |magazine=Rolling Stone |date=2016-01-10 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170215034423/http://www.rollingstone.com/tv/news/lady-gaga-i-wanted-to-be-an-actress-before-a-singer-20160110 |archivedate=2017-02-15 }}</ref> 自2015年10月播放至2016年1月，《旅館》是恐怖獨立單元劇系列《[[美國恐怖故事|美國恐怖故事]]》的第五季，其中，卡卡飾演著酒店的老闆[[美國恐怖故事：旅館#演員|伊莉莎白]]。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/09/10/entertainment/american-horror-story-hotel-trailer-feat-thr/|title=Lady Gaga joins American Horror Story Season 5|first=Dana Rose|last=Falcone|publisher=CNN|date=2015-09-10|accessdate=2016-02-26|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150914025840/http://www.cnn.com/2015/09/10/entertainment/american-horror-story-hotel-trailer-feat-thr|archivedate=2015-09-14}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/2727963/american-horror-story-hotel-finale/|publisher=MTV News|date=2016-01-13|accessdate=2017-08-31|title='American Horror Story': 7 Things We Need To See In The 'Hotel' Finale|first=Shaunna|last=Murphy|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170831222444/http://www.mtv.com/news/2727963/american-horror-story-hotel-finale/|archivedate=2017-08-31}}</ref> 在[[第73屆金球獎|第73屆金球獎]]中，卡卡於當屆榮獲{{link-en|金球獎最佳迷你影集或電視電影女主角|Golden Globe Award for Best Actress – Miniseries or Television Film|最佳迷你影集或電視電影女主角}}。<ref name=GoldenGlobeAHS/> 同年，卡卡參與了攝影師尼克·奈特為設計師[[湯姆·福特|湯姆·福特]]設於隔年的春季活動而著手進行的攝影計畫。<ref>{{cite news |last=Piere |first=Kerry |title=Tom Ford Debuts Spring 2016 With Lady Gaga |url=http://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/fashion-week/news/a12382/tom-ford-spring-2016-fashion-show/ |work=[[Harper's_Bazaar|Harper's Bazaar]] |date=2015-10-02 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20160316070444/http://www.harpersbazaar.com/fashion/fashion-week-fall-2016/news/a12382/tom-ford-spring-2016-fashion-show/ |archivedate=2016-03-16 |accessdate=2017-11-07 }}</ref> 而隔年1月，她受邀自時尚雜誌《{{tsl|en|V (American magazine)|V}}》以客串編輯的身分加入雜誌出版第99集的製作，其中，他們拍攝並選用了16不同的封面。<ref name="V mag">{{cite magazine|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6836129/lady-gaga-taylor-kinney-v-magazine-naked-john-yoko|access-date=2016-01-08|date=2016-01-08|title=Lady Gaga & Taylor Kinney Are Naked & 'Making Love for Peace' on New Mag Cover|magazine=Billboard|first=Jessie|last=Katz|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160108184530/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/6836129/lady-gaga-taylor-kinney-v-magazine-naked-john-yoko|archive-date=2016-01-08}}</ref> 同年，她於洛杉磯時尚獎榮獲「年度編輯獎」。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.etonline.com/news/184867_lady_gaga_nabs_editor_of_the_year_at_fashion_los_angeles_awards/ |title=Lady Gaga Nabs Editor of the Year at Fashion Los Angeles Awards |date=2016-03-21 |work=[[Entertainment_Tonight|Entertainment Tonight]] |last1=Krauser |first1=Emily |accessdate=2016-03-24 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160326020125/http://www.etonline.com/news/184867_lady_gaga_nabs_editor_of_the_year_at_fashion_los_angeles_awards/ |archivedate=2016-03-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

