rter |last=Gardner |first=Chris |date=2016-02-04 |accessdate=2016-02-04 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160205092622/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/lady-gaga-be-honored-by-861971 |archivedate=2016-02-05 }}</ref> 到了7月，卡卡與未婚夫泰勒·金尼取消訂婚；而她本人也於事後表示她的事業已經嚴重干擾到兩人之間的關係了。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/3035684/lady-gaga-taylor-kinney-relationship-doc/|title=Lady Gaga Says Her Success Led To Her Breakup With Taylor Kinney|first=Emilee|last=Lindner|publisher=MTV News|date=2017-09-12|accessdate=2017-11-19|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170930041349/http://www.mtv.com/news/3035684/lady-gaga-taylor-kinney-relationship-doc/|archivedate=2017-09-30}}</ref> 

6月27日，卡卡出席位於印地安納波里斯的第84屆美國市長會議。並在其中一場座談會上與[[第十四世达赖喇嘛|第十四世达赖喇嘛]]會面，兩人的對談於臉書上直播，並在於事後於[[Instagram|Instagram]]發出她和達賴的合照，她引述達賴的話留言「要讓世界運轉，希望是必要的」(Hope is essential to keep the world going)。此舉引起中国粉絲反彈，他們表示「国家面前无偶像」並抵制卡卡<ref>{{cite news |editor=林西 |title=Lady Gaga晒与达赖同台合影引众怒 网友：国家面前无偶像 |url=https://www.guancha.cn/local/2016_06_27_365573_s.shtml |accessdate=2021-03-30 |work=观察者网 |date=2016-06-27 |archive-date=2021-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511111319/https://www.guancha.cn/local/2016_06_27_365573_s.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |author1=林鹏飞 |author2=吴志伟 |author3=任重 |title=Lady Gaga与达赖喇嘛见面 外媒关注中国网民声讨Lady Gaga |url=https://world.huanqiu.com/article/9CaKrnJWam8 |accessdate=2021-03-30 |work=环球时报 |date=2016-06-29 |archive-date=2021-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210511112807/https://world.huanqiu.com/article/9CaKrnJWam8 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。有媒体报道指，中華人民共和国隨後封杀了女神卡卡。<ref>{{cite web|title=英媒：嘎嘎小姐會見達賴喇嘛被中國「封殺」|url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/press_review/2016/06/160628_press_review_lady_gaga|work=BBC中文网|accessdate=2016年6月28日|archive-date=2019年6月16日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190616133140/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/press_review/2016/06/160628_press_review_lady_gaga|dead-url=no}}</ref>雖有消息称[[中央宣傳部|中央宣傳部]]等國家機構要求中国媒體立即停播、上传卡卡的作品，並禁售與之相關產品。但卡卡2013年发行的新专辑《[[流行藝術|流行藝術]]》仍獲准於中國發行<ref>{{cite web|title=Lady Gaga見達賴　遭中共封殺|url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20160628/19672745|work=香港蘋果日報|accessdate=2016年6月28日|archive-date=2017年3月7日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170307083212/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/international/art/20160628/19672745|dead-url=no}}</ref>。据法新社等報道，[[中國外交部發言人|中國外交部發言人]][[洪磊|洪磊]]于6月27日例行记者会表示，自己不認識女神卡卡，并表示「希望國際社會認清達賴的真實面目和本質」<ref>{{cite web|title=Lady Gaga與達賴見面 網民聲討|url=http://news.wenweipo.com/2016/06/29/IN1606290005.htm|work=香港文汇报|accessdate=2016年6月29日|archive-date=2020年11月20日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120080920/http://news.wenweipo.com/2016/06/29/IN1606290005.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但在中國外交部网站刊载的外交部发言记者会的报道里，並無提及此事。<ref>{{cite web|title=2016年6月27日外交部发言人洪磊主持例行记者会|url=http://www.mfa.gov.cn/web/fyrbt_673021/t1375534.shtml|work=中华人民共和国外交部|accessdate=2016年6月29日|archive-date=2020年3月24日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200324092203/https://www.mfa.gov.cn/web/fyrbt_673021/t1375534.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

卡卡再度於《[[美國恐怖故事|美國恐怖故事]]》演出，並於第六季《[[美國恐怖故事：羅亞諾克|羅阿諾克]]》中飾演巫女斯卡薩哈，<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.harpersbazaar.com/culture/film-tv/reviews/a18107/american-horror-story-season-6-episode-4-recap/ |title=8 Things We Learned From 'American Horror Story: Roanoke' Chapter 4 |last=Diblin |first=Emma |date=2016-10-06 |accessdate=2016-10-13 |work=Harper's Bazaar |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161013224158/http://www.harpersbazaar.com/culture/film-tv/reviews/a18107/american-horror-story-season-6-episode-4-recap/ |archivedate=2016-10-13 }}</ref> 該季影集於同年9月播至同年11月。<ref>{{cite magazine |last1=Snetiker |first1=Marc |title=American Horror Story 6 premiere recap: 'Chapter 1' |magazine=Entertainment Weekly |date=2016-09-15 |url=http://www.ew.com/recap/american-horror-story-season-6-premiere |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161226222323/http://ew.com/recap/american-horror-story-season-6-premiere/ |archivedate=2016-12-26 |accessdate=2017-11-07 }}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine |last1=Stedman |first1=Alex |title='American Horror Story' Season Finale Recap: 'Chapter 10' Reveals the True Survivor of 'Roanoke' |magazine=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]] |date=2016-11-16 |url=https://variety.com/2016/tv/news/american-horror-story-roanoke-finale-recap-season-6-episode-10-1201920109/ |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161220190137/http://variety.com/2016/tv/news/american-horror-story-roanoke-finale-recap-season-6-episode-10-1201920109/ |archivedate=2016-12-20 |accessdate=2017-11-07 }}</ref> 卡卡於第五季中演出的角色在最後甚至影響了她未來的音樂風格，促使她以「音樂的黑暗性」為特色。<ref>{{cite magazine|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2015/08/27/lady-gaga-american-horror-story-music|title=Lady Gaga Says American Horror Story Experience Will 'Inform' Her Upcoming Music|last=Stack|first=Tim|magazine=Entertainment Weekly|date=2015-08-27|accessdate=2015-08-29|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150828133408/http://www.ew.com/article/2015/08/27/lady-gaga-american-horror-story-music|archivedate=2015-08-28}}</ref> 9月時，她發行了第五張個人專輯的首單《[[完美幻象|完美幻象]]》(Perfect Illusion) ，該曲首周於美國榜單排行第15名。<ref>{{cite magazine|title=Lady Gaga Joanne release date: New album will be out Oct. 21|url=http://ew.com/article/2016/09/15/lady-gaga-joanne-release-date/|first=Allison|last=Sadlier|magazine=Entertainment Weekly|date=2016-09-15|accessdate=2017-11-12|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171113114728/http://ew.com/article/2016/09/15/lady-gaga-joanne-release-date/|archivedate=2017-11-13}}</ref><ref name=SuperBowlResult>{{cite magazine |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/7686444/hot-100-ed-sheeran-shape-of-you-lady-gaga-million-reasons |title=Ed Sheeran's 'Shape' Tops Hot 100, Lady Gaga's 'Reasons' Returns at No. 4 |first=Gary |last=Trust |magazine=Billboard |date=2017-02-13 |accessdate=2017-02-13 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170213221900/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/7686444/hot-100-ed-sheeran-shape-of-you-lady-gaga-million-reasons |archivedate=2017-02-13 }}</ref> 專輯名為《[[喬安_(女神卡卡專輯)|喬安]]》（原文: Joanne），靈感源自於啟發她音樂靈感的，已逝世的同名姑姑。<ref>{{cite magazine|last=Redfearn|first=Dominique|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/7511076/lady-gaga-joanne-story-behind-album-title|title=Who Is Joanne? Behind Lady Gaga's New Album Title|magazine=Billboard|date=2016-09-15|accessdate=2016-10-15|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161009204449/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/7511076/lady-gaga-joanne-story-behind-album-title|archivedate=2016-10-09}}</ref> 10月21日，專輯藉著首周17萬份的成績成為了卡卡在《告示牌》中第四張冠軍專輯，也使她成為了美國2010年後第一位擁有四張冠軍專輯的女性。<ref>{{cite magazine |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/7557828/lady-gaga-scores-her-fourth-no-1-album-on-billboard-200-chart-joanne |title=Lady Gaga Scores Her Fourth No. 1 Album on Billboard 200 Chart With 'Joanne' |first=Keith |last=Caulfield |date=2016-10-30 |accessdate=2016-10-30 |magazine=Billboard |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161030194903/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/7557828/lady-gaga-scores-her-fourth-no-1-album-on-billboard-200-chart-joanne |archivedate=2016-10-30 }}</ref> 隔月，專輯的第二張單曲《[[百萬個理由|百萬個理由]]》(Million Reason) 正式發行，於美國榜單排行第4。<ref name=SuperBowlResult/><ref>{{cite magazine |url=http://ew.com/article/2016/11/07/kelsea-ballerini-lady-gaga-million-reasons-cover/ |title=Kelsea Ballerini covers Lady Gaga's Million Reasons |last=Nolfi |first=Joey |date=2016-11-07 |accessdate=2017-08-03 |magazine=Entertainment Weekly |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170803125851/http://ew.com/article/2016/11/07/kelsea-ballerini-lady-gaga-million-reasons-cover/ |archivedate=2017-08-03 }}</ref> 《喬安》和《百萬個理由》分別於葛萊美獎中提名為最佳流行演唱專輯以及最佳流行歌手。<ref>{{cite magazine|last1=Lynch|first1=Joe|title=Grammys 2018: See the Complete List of Nominees|magazine=Billboard|date=2017-11-28|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/grammys/8047027/grammys-2018-complete-nominees-list|accessdate=2018-02-04|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171128164605/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/grammys/8047027/grammys-2018-complete-nominees-list|archivedate=2017-11-28}}</ref> 為了宣傳專輯，卡卡開始了僅有3個場次的[[Dive_Bar_Tour|Dive Bar巡迴演唱會]]。<ref>{{cite magazine |last=McIntyre |first=Hugh |url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/hughmcintyre/2016/10/02/15171/ |title=Lady Gaga Is Going On Tour To Dive Bars Across America |magazine=[[Forbes|Forbes]] |date=2016-10-02 |accessdate=2016-10-07 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161006205319/http://www.forbes.com/sites/hughmcintyre/2016/10/02/15171/ |archivedate=2016-10-06 }}</ref>

隔年2月5日，卡卡主持並於{{tsl|en|Super Bowl LI halftime show|第五十一屆超級盃中場秀}}演出。她的表演配上了數百台的設有照明裝置的無人機在休士頓[[NRG體育場|NRG體育場]]的上空組成多中不同的形狀，這同時也是飛行無人機首次出現在超級盃的計畫節目中。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.foxnews.com/entertainment/2017/02/05/lady-gaga-super-bowl-halftime-show-to-feature-hundreds-drones-in-aerial-light-show.html |title=Lady Gaga Super Bowl halftime show to feature hundreds of drones in aerial light show |date=2017-02-05 |publisher=[[Fox_News_Channel|Fox News Channel]] |accessdate=2017-06-08 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170519045714/http://www.foxnews.com/entertainment/2017/02/05/lady-gaga-super-bowl-halftime-show-to-feature-hundreds-drones-in-aerial-light-show.html |archivedate=2017-05-19 }}</ref> 這表演在美國吸引了總計1.175億的觀看次數，超過了球賽本身總計1.133億的觀看次數。<ref>{{cite magazine |title=Super Bowl LI Pulls in 111.3 Million Viewers on Fox, Shy of 2015 Ratings Record |url=https://variety.com/2017/tv/news/super-bowl-li-ratings-patriots-falcons-24-1201978629/ |magazine=Variety |date=2017-02-06 |deadurl=yes |first=Oriana |last=Schwindt |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170206140641/http://variety.com/2017/tv/news/super-bowl-li-ratings-patriots-falcons-24-1201978629/ |archivedate=2017-02-06 |access-date=2018-09-20 }}</ref> 該場表演讓卡卡在美國內部的歌曲下載次數激增了41萬，並同時讓她獲[[艾美獎|艾美獎]]提名為{{tsl|en|Primetime Emmy Award for Outstanding Special Class Program|最佳特別節目}}。<ref>{{cite magazine|title=Lady Gaga's Super Week: Her Sales & Streaming Gains After the Big Game|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/7694020/lady-gaga-super-bowl-sales-streaming-gains-songs-albums|accessdate=2017-02-16|magazine=Billboard|date=2017-02-16|last=Caulfield|first=Keith|last2=Trust|first2=Gary|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170216154053/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/7694020/lady-gaga-super-bowl-sales-streaming-gains-songs-albums|archivedate=2017-02-16}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.refinery29.com/2017/07/163326/lady-gaga-2017-emmys-superbowl-halftime-show|title=Lady Gaga's Super Bowl Performance Casually Rakes In Six Emmy Noms|last=Rhiannon|first=Alexis|date=2017-07-14|accessdate=2017-07-19|publisher=[[Refinery29|Refinery29]]|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170714020215/http://www.refinery29.com/2017/07/163326/lady-gaga-2017-emmys-superbowl-halftime-show|archivedate=2017-07-14}}</ref> [[CBS體育|CBS體育]]整理了歷年來的超級盃表演，其中卡卡位列第2名。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Peterson|first1=Nate|title=2018 Super Bowl halftime show: Ranking every performance, from Prince to Coldplay|url=https://www.cbssports.com/nfl/news/2018-super-bowl-halftime-show-ranking-every-performance-from-prince-to-coldplay/|publisher=[[CBS_Sports|CBS Sports]]|accessdate=2018-02-04|date=2018-02-04|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180204183142/https://www.cbssports.com/nfl/news/2018-super-bowl-halftime-show-ranking-every-performance-from-prince-to-coldplay/|archivedate=2018-02-04}}</ref> 同年四月，卡卡主持了[[科切拉音樂節|科切拉音樂節]]。<ref name="Coachella">{{cite magazine |url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/business/7709328/how-coachella-booked-lady-gaga-beyonce-reaction-inside-story |title=How Coachella Gained Lady Gaga After Losing Beyonce |magazine=Billboard |first=Dave |last=Brooks |date=2017-03-02 |accessdate=2017-03-02 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170302205129/http://www.billboard.com/articles/business/7709328/how-coachella-booked-lady-gaga-beyonce-reaction-inside-story |archivedate=2017-03-02 }}</ref> 她同時在表演時釋出了獨立單曲《{{tsl|en|The Cure (song)|解藥}}》(The Cure) ，單曲發行後於法國及澳洲榜單排行前10。<ref>{{cite magazine |url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/watch-lady-gaga-debut-new-single-the-cure-at-coachella-w477048 |title=Watch Lady Gaga Debut Surprise New Single 'The Cure' at Coachella |magazine=Rolling Stone |first=Daniel |last=Kreps |date=2017-04-16 |accessdate=2017-06-08 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170517095010/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/watch-lady-gaga-debut-new-single-the-cure-at-coachella-w477048 |archivedate=2017-05-17 }}</ref><ref>Chart positions for "The Cure":
* {{cite web|title=Australian-charts.com – Lady Gaga – The Cure|url=http://www.australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Lady+Gaga&titel=The+Cure&cat=s|publisher=Hung Medien|accessdate=2017-11-07|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170924001702/http://www.australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Lady+Gaga&titel=The+Cure&cat=s|archivedate=2017-09-24}}
* {{cite web|title=Lescharts.com – Lady Gaga – The Cure|url=http://www.lescharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Lady+Gaga&titel=The+Cure&cat=s|publisher=Hung Medien|accessdate=2017-11-07|language=fr|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107221842/http://www.lescharts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Lady+Gaga&titel=The+Cure&cat=s|archivedate=2017-11-07}}</ref> 四個月後，卡卡開始了在超級盃中場秀後宣布的[[喬安世界巡迴演唱會|喬安世界巡迴演唱會]]。<ref name=tickets>{{cite web |url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/lady-gaga-announces-joanne-world-tour-after-hit-packed-super-bowl-halftime-show__18097/ |title=Lady Gaga announces Joanne world tour after hit-packed Super Bowl Halftime Show |publisher=Official Charts Company |first=Rob |last=Copsey |date=2016-02-06 |accessdate=2017-02-06 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170206185158/http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/lady-gaga-announces-joanne-world-tour-after-hit-packed-super-bowl-halftime-show__18097/ |archivedate=2017-02-06 }}</ref> 11月，以卡卡製作《喬安》以及超級盃中場秀的準備過程為主題的紀錄片《女神卡卡：五呎二吋》，於[[Netflix|Netflix]]首次亮相。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Kaufman|first1=Amy|title=Lady Gaga's five most revealing moments in the Netflix documentary 'Gaga: Five Foot Two'|url=http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/la-et-mn-toronto-lady-gaga-five-foot-two-20170908-story.html|accessdate=2017-10-27|newspaper=Los Angeles Times|date=2017-09-08|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171027232540/http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/movies/la-et-mn-toronto-lady-gaga-five-foot-two-20170908-story.html|archivedate=2017-10-27}}</ref> 透過電影，可以了解她已經多年因[[慢性疼痛|慢性疼痛]]—後期發現是名為纖維肌痛症的慢性病的影響而苦。<ref>{{cite web |last=Gonzalez |first=Sandra |title=Lady Gaga will open up about fight with chronic illness in Netflix documentary |url=http://edition.cnn.com/2017/09/12/entertainment/lady-gaga-fibromyalgia/index.html |publisher=CNN |date=2017-09-13 |accessdate=2017-09-15 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170914141100/http://edition.cnn.com/2017/09/12/entertainment/lady-gaga-fibromyalgia/index.html |archivedate=2017-09-14 }}</ref> 這也導致卡卡取消了喬安世界巡迴演唱會的最後十場場次，該巡演總共賣出了84萬2千張票，總銷售額為9.5千萬美元<ref>{{cite magazine|last1=Kreps|first1=Daniel|title=Lady Gaga Cancels Remainder of Joanne World Tour Due to 'Severe Pain'|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/lady-gaga-cancels-remainder-of-world-tour-due-to-severe-pain-w516312|accessdate=2018-02-04|magazine=Rolling Stone|date=2018-02-03|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180204050645/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/lady-gaga-cancels-remainder-of-world-tour-due-to-severe-pain-w516312|archivedate=2018-02-04}}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine|last1=Allen|first1=Bob|title=Lady Gaga's Joanne World Tour Final Numbers: $95 Million Earned & 842,000 Tickets Sold|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/8099986/lady-gaga-joanne-world-tour-final-numbers|accessdate=2018-02-25|magazine=Billboard|date=2018-02-15|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180216123848/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/chart-beat/8099986/lady-gaga-joanne-world-tour-final-numbers|archivedate=2018-02-16}}</ref>。

