同年3月，卡卡發聲表示支持於首都[[华盛顿哥伦比亚特区|華府]]進行的，由高中生發起的[[槍枝管制|槍枝管制]]聲訴活動 March for Our Lives。<ref>{{cite magazine|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/8259218/jennifer-lopez-jimmy-fallon-lady-gaga-sponsor-buses-to-march-for-our-lives-gun-control-violence|title=Jennifer Lopez, Jimmy Fallon, Lady Gaga Sponsor Buses to March for Our Lives|first=Katie|last=Kilkenny|magazine=Billboard|date=2018-03-24|accessdate=2018-05-09|archive-date=2018-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180511184446/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/8259218/jennifer-lopez-jimmy-fallon-lady-gaga-sponsor-buses-to-march-for-our-lives-gun-control-violence|dead-url=no}}</ref> 並同時釋出了收錄於知名歌手[[艾爾頓·強|艾爾頓·強]]的致敬專輯《Revamp》中的歌曲《Your Song》翻唱版。<ref>{{cite news|last1=Kreps|first1=Daniel|title=Hear Lady Gaga's Powerful Take on Elton John's 'Your Song'|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/hear-lady-gagas-powerful-take-on-elton-johns-your-song-w518545|accessdate=2018-03-30|work=Rolling Stone|date=2018-03-30|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180330164158/https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/hear-lady-gagas-powerful-take-on-elton-johns-your-song-w518545|archivedate=2018-03-30|deadurl=no}}</ref> 之後，她本人宣布正在參與由男演員[[布萊德利·庫柏|布萊德利·庫柏]]翻拍自電影《星海浮沉錄》(1937年) 的最新版本 (2018年)。電影中，她所飾演的新人歌手艾莉在劇中與資深歌手傑克森·緬因 (布萊德利·庫柏飾演)相戀，但其戀情卻因為艾莉的事業成就高過傑克森而開始產生裂痕。<ref>{{cite magazine |last1=Lang |first1=Brent |title=First Look at Lady Gaga and Bradley Cooper in 'A Star Is Born' |magazine=Variety |date=2017-04-17 |url=https://variety.com/2017/film/news/lady-gaga-bradley-cooper-star-is-born-photo-1202032227/ |accessdate=2017-07-13 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170426225059/http://variety.com/2017/film/news/lady-gaga-bradley-cooper-star-is-born-photo-1202032227/ |archivedate=2017-04-26 }}</ref> 庫柏看到卡卡於癌症研究募捐活動的表演後便試著與她接觸；卡卡表示當初她會同意這項計畫是因為她非常讚賞庫柏的作品以及電影劇本中對[[成癮行為|成癮]]和[[抑鬱症|抑鬱]]的描寫。<ref>{{cite news|title='A Star Is Born': Our intimate conversation with Lady Gaga and Bradley Cooper|url=https://ew.com/movies/2018/08/31/a-star-is-born-lady-gaga-bradley-cooper-interview/|accessdate=2018-08-31|work=Entertainment Weekly|date=2018-08-31|archive-date=2018-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180901112537/https://ew.com/movies/2018/08/31/a-star-is-born-lady-gaga-bradley-cooper-interview/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine|last1=Tailor|first1=Leena|title=How Lady Gaga Conquered Music, Fashion and Film in Just a Decade|url=https://www.etonline.com/how-lady-gaga-conquered-music-fashion-and-film-fall-preview-106993|accessdate=2018-09-04|magazine=Entertainment Tonight|date=2018-09-04|archive-date=2018-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180904225726/https://www.etonline.com/how-lady-gaga-conquered-music-fashion-and-film-fall-preview-106993|dead-url=no}}</ref> 同年8月，該片於[[第75屆威尼斯影展|第75屆威尼斯影展]]首次亮相，並隨後將在 10月於全球同步釋出。<ref>{{cite magazine |title=Venice: Lady Gaga on Bradley Cooper Bringing Out Her "Vulnerability" for 'A Star Is Born' |url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/lady-gaga-acting-debut-bradley-coopers-a-star-is-born-venice-film-festival-1138897 |accessdate=2018-08-31 |work=The Hollywood Reporter |date=2018-08-31 |archive-date=2018-08-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180831160321/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/lady-gaga-acting-debut-bradley-coopers-a-star-is-born-venice-film-festival-1138897 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 《[[衛報|衛報]]》的彼得‧布萊德修以「驚人的可觀」形容這部片並提到「卡卡飾演平凡人至外星名人女皇的能力達到最高水準。」<ref>{{cite news |last1=Bradshaw |first1=Peter |title=A Star Is Born review – Lady Gaga mesmerises in Streisand's shoes |url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2018/aug/31/a-star-is-born-review-lady-gaga-bradley-cooper |accessdate=2018-08-31 |work=The Guardian |date=2018-08-31 |archive-date=2018-08-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180831185911/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2018/aug/31/a-star-is-born-review-lady-gaga-bradley-cooper |dead-url=no }}</ref> 雜誌《[[時代雜誌|時代]]》的史蒂芬妮‧札克雷克與前者一樣強調並讚美她「強力的演技」，並同時讚美她在片中發現到當卡卡卸下妝容、假髮和衣著時所具有的「獨特魅力」。<ref>{{cite magazine |title=Lady Gaga Delivers a Knockout Performance in 'A Star Is Born' |url=http://time.com/5382763/a-star-is-born-review/ |accessdate=2018-08-31 |magazine=Time |date=2018-08-31 |archive-date=2018-08-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180831225603/http://time.com/5382763/a-star-is-born-review/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> 除了奧斯卡獎[[奧斯卡最佳女主角獎|最佳女主角]]的提名，卡卡以飾演女主角艾莉贏得了[[評論家選擇電影獎最佳女主角|評論家選擇電影獎]]以及{{tsl|en|National Board of Review Award for Best Actress|國家評論協會獎最佳女主角|國家評論協會}}的獎項，並於[[英國電影學院獎最佳女主角|英國電影學院獎]]、[[金球奖剧情类电影最佳女主角|金球獎]]以及[[美國演員工會獎最佳女主角|美國演員工會獎]]獎項提名。<ref name="a star is born awards and nominations">Awards and nominations for ''A Star Is Born'':

