rack-nominees/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 同月25日，卡卡於[[奥斯卡金像奖|奧斯卡金像獎]]頒獎禮上與[[布萊德利·庫柏|布萊德利·庫柏]]首次於電視直播上合唱《淺灘》，並憑《淺灘》獲頒最佳原創歌曲。<ref>{{Cite web|title=【奧斯卡】《星夢情深》Lady Gaga奪最佳主題曲 (11:55) - 20190225 - SHOWBIZ|url=https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20190225/1551066904895/%e3%80%90%e5%a5%a7%e6%96%af%e5%8d%a1%e3%80%91%e3%80%8a%e6%98%9f%e5%a4%a2%e6%83%85%e6%b7%b1%e3%80%8blady-gaga%e5%a5%aa%e6%9c%80%e4%bd%b3%e4%b8%bb%e9%a1%8c%e6%9b%b2|work=明報OL網|accessdate=2019-02-27|language=zh-hant|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120081548/https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20190225/1551066904895/%E3%80%90%E5%A5%A7%E6%96%AF%E5%8D%A1%E3%80%91%E3%80%8A%E6%98%9F%E5%A4%A2%E6%83%85%E6%B7%B1%E3%80%8Blady-gaga%E5%A5%AA%E6%9C%80%E4%BD%B3%E4%B8%BB%E9%A1%8C%E6%9B%B2|dead-url=no}}</ref> 典禮完結後，卡卡前往瑪丹娜主辦的派對並拍下合照引起粉絲及媒體議論。<ref>{{Cite web|title=LADY GAGA AND MADONNA END FEUD|url=https://ewn.co.za/2019/02/26/lady-gaga-and-madonna-end-feud/|work=Eyewitness News|accessdate=2019-03-01|language=en|archive-date=2020-10-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201001045748/https://ewn.co.za/2019/02/26/lady-gaga-and-madonna-end-feud|dead-url=no}}</ref> 包含以上3項獎項，單曲使卡卡贏得了[[金球獎最佳原創歌曲|金球獎]]和{{tsl|en|Critics' Choice Movie Award for Best Song|廣播影評人協會獎最佳歌曲|評論家選擇電影獎}}等最佳原創歌曲獎。並同時使卡卡成為史上第一位藝人及第一首歌曲於同一獎季贏得[[金球獎|金球獎]]、[[葛萊美獎|葛萊美獎]]、[[英国电影学院奖|英國電影學院獎]]及[[奥斯卡金像奖|奧斯卡金像獎]]<ref name="a star is born awards and nominations"/>，並超越歌手[[碧昂絲|碧昂絲]]的《女力來襲》（Formation）成為史上獲獎最多的歌曲，至今共獲得32項官方獎項。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.mensxp.com/entertainment/hollywood/50589-lady-gaga-won-an-oscar-for-lsquo-shallow-rsquo-created-history-by-making-it-the-most-awarded-song-ever.html|title=Lady Gaga Won An Oscar For 'Shallow' & Created History By Making It The Most Awarded Song Ever|date=2019-02-25|accessdate=2019-03-01|publisher=MensXP|archive-date=2020-12-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201227190124/https://www.mensxp.com/entertainment/hollywood/50589-lady-gaga-won-an-oscar-for-lsquo-shallow-rs