2018年，卡卡簽下了為期兩年的駐唱合約，並於[[拉斯維加斯|拉斯維加斯]]的[[蒙地卡羅賭場度假村|公園劇場]]舉辦演唱會《女神卡卡: 謎》。<ref name="ewenigma">{{cite magazine|url=http://ew.com/music/2018/08/07/lady-gaga-las-vegas-residency-details/|title=Lady Gaga announces Las Vegas residency show details|last=Nolfi|first=Joel|date=2018-08-07|accessdate=2018-08-07|magazine=Entertainment Weekly|archive-date=2018-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180808181342/https://ew.com/music/2018/08/07/lady-gaga-las-vegas-residency-details/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 駐唱由兩種不同類型的演唱會組成: 以戲劇性和卡卡熱門歌曲為主要焦點的《謎》，<ref>{{cite news|last=Hale|first=Andreas|title=Lady Gaga Delivers the Show She Was Born to Perform With 'Enigma'|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/8491731/lady-gaga-enigma-opening-night-review|accessdate=2019-01-23|work=Billboard|date=2018-12-29|archive-date=2019-01-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190112085906/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/8491731/lady-gaga-enigma-opening-night-review|dead-url=no}}</ref> 以及以選自{{tsl|en|Great American Songbook|美國金曲簿}}的歌曲以及爵士版的卡卡的歌曲為主的《爵士與鋼琴》。《謎》駐唱表演於2018年12月28日首次開唱，《爵士與鋼琴》則於隔年1月20日開唱。<ref>{{cite news|last=Wood|first=Mikael|title=Review: In Las Vegas, Lady Gaga solves the problem of 'A Star Is Born'|url=https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/music/la-et-ms-lady-gaga-enigma-jazz-piano-las-vegas-review-20190121-story.html|accessdate=2019-01-23|work=[[Los_Angeles_Times|Los Angeles Times]]|date=2019-01-21|archive-date=2019-01-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190122120331/https://www.latimes.com/entertainment/music/la-et-ms-lady-gaga-enigma-jazz-piano-las-vegas-review-20190121-story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 2019年9月，卡卡於亞馬遜上發行她的首款純素化妝品系列Haus Laboratories。由40款產品組成，包含液體眼線筆、唇彩和臉部貼紙，產品在亞馬遜的暢銷口紅榜單上排行第一。<ref>{{cite web |last1=Thompson |first1=Courtney |title=Lady Gaga's new holiday lipstick is already No. 1 on Amazon |url=https://us.cnn.com/2019/11/22/cnn-underscored/lady-gaga-haus-sparkle-lipstick/index.html |publisher=CNN |access-date=2019-12-06 |language=en |date=2019-11-23 |archive-date=2020-11-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201126064232/https://us.cnn.com/2019/11/22/cnn-underscored/lady-gaga-haus-sparkle-lipstick/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> 隔年2月，卡卡開始與企業家麥可·波蘭斯基交往。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/9361099/lady-gaga-says-boyfriend-michael-polansky-is-the-love-of-my-life |last1=Peters |first1=Mitchell |title=Lady Gaga Says Boyfriend Michael Polansky Is the 'Love of My Life': Watch |date=2020-04-18 |access-date=2020-04-19 |website=[[Billboard_(magazine)|Billboard]] |archive-url=https://archive.today/20200522102827/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/9361099/lady-gaga-says-boyfriend-michael-polansky-is-the-love-of-my-life |archive-date=2020-05-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 卡卡於2020年2月25日在社群媒體宣布新專輯《神彩》（原文: Chromatica）於2020年4月10日發售，後因[[COVID-19|COVID-19疫情]]宣布延期至5月29日發售。<ref>{{cite web |title=Lady Gaga Postpones Release of New Album Chromatica |url=https://consequenceofsound.net/2020/03/lady-gaga-postpones-release-of-new-album-chromatica/ |website=[[Consequence_of_Sounds|Consequence of Sounds]] |publisher= |accessdate=2020-03-25 |dead-url=no |archive-date=2020-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130151113/https://consequenceofsound.net/2020/03/lady-gaga-postpones-release-of-new-album-chromatica/ }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Rettig |first=James |title=Lady Gaga's ''Chromatica'' Is Now Out 5/29 |url=https://www.stereogum.com/2083513/lady-gaga-chromatica-release-date-change/news/ |website=[[Stereogum|Stereogum]] |publisher=[[Valence_Media|Valence Media]] |accessdate=2020-05-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200506161939/https://www.stereogum.com/2083513/lady-gaga-chromatica-release-date-change/news/ |archivedate=2020-05-06 |date=2020-05-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 並在此前發行兩張單曲，2月28日的《癡癡的愛》(Stupid Love)，<ref>{{cite news|last=Rowley|first=Glenn|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/8551871/lady-gaga-confirms-release-date-stupid-love|title=Lady Gaga Is About to Drop Her New Single 'Stupid Love' and We Are Not Calm: Find Out the Release Date|magazine=[[Billboard_(magazine)|Billboard]]|date=2020-02-25|accessdate=2020-02-25|archive-date=2020-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120081628/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/8551871/lady-gaga-confirms-release-date-stupid-love|dead-url=no}}</ref> 以及5月22日，和[[亞莉安娜·格蘭德|亞莉安娜·格蘭德]]合作的《讓雨降臨》(Rain on Me)。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/9379055/lady-gaga-ariana-grande-rain-on-me-release-date|title=Lady Gaga & Ariana Grande's 'Rain on Me' Collaboration Is Coming Really Soon|last=Aniftos|first=Rania|website=[[Billboard_(magazine)|Billboard]]|date=2020-05-15|accessdate=2020-05-16|archive-date=2020-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200515235931/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop/9379055/lady-gaga-ariana-grande-rain-on-me-release-date|dead-url=no}}</ref> 後者於美國空降第一，讓卡卡成為第三名分別在2000年代、2010年代和2020年代登上該國榜首的人。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/business/chart-beat/9394719/rain-on-me-debuts-atop-hot-100-lady-gaga-ariana-grande|title=Lady Gaga & Ariana Grande's 'Rain on Me' Debuts at No. 1 on Billboard Hot 100|work=[[Billboard_(magazine)|Billboard]]|last=Trust|first=Gary|date=2020-06-01|accessdate=2020-06-01|archive-date=2020-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200603055218/https://www.billboard.com/articles/business/chart-beat/9394719/rain-on-me-debuts-atop-hot-100-lady-gaga-ariana-grande|dead-url=no}}</ref> 隨了憑着《星夢情深》（A Star Is Born）入圍金球影后，她也憑着電影歌曲爭奪4項格林美獎，加上個人歌曲獎提名，一共獲得5項《第61屆格林美獎》提名。<ref>{{cite news |author1=東方日報 |title=GaGa延續金球氣勢擸格林美5提名 |url=https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20181209/00288_001.html |accessdate=2020-07-30 |archive-date=2020-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201120081629/https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20181209/00288_001.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

